{"tid":1488320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HK Free Press - 一個需要大家支持既香港英文媒體","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T13:23:03.000Z","uid":220977,"like":124,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"6cff47c5b5884262080f4c62ee90fba90d8a5bb6","tid":1488320,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"雖然我係首席RTHK打手,琴日又開po吹奏立場哥哥<br />\n但今日希望大家可以關注下HONG KONG FREE PRESS<br />\n<br />\n國際輿論係我地其中一個重要戰線,英文既新聞coverage 係好重要，google &lsquo;hong kong protests&rsquo;既results 全部都係新聞<br />\n<br />\n雖然外媒都好關注今次既運動<br />\n但始終佢地唔會好似本地媒體咁跟到咁貼<br />\n大家都知本港最大英文媒體SCMP係紅底<br />\n雖然某d記者係ok但有時d評論報導嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地需要獨立英文媒體既報導！<br />\n<br />\nHKFP 係一個香港based既英文媒體,完全獨立,非牟利<br />\n佢地都有廣泛cover 反送中：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/category/topics/politics-protest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fcategory%2Ftopics%2Fpolitics-protest%2F&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=b772dbc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/category/topics/politics-protest/</a><br />\n<br />\n有d 評論都寫得幾好，都有share俾外國朋友睇<br />\n例如： <a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/08/11/complain-hong-kongs-anti-extradition-bill-protesters-consider/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F08%2F11%2Fcomplain-hong-kongs-anti-extradition-bill-protesters-consider%2F&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=f0b271df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/08/11/complain-hong-kongs-anti-extradition-bill-protesters-consider/</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩突發野佢地都會開live,會用英文做旁白<br />\n<br />\n佢地係獨立，非牟利，靠眾籌support營運<br />\n<br />\n希望大家課金俾立場之餘都可以分少少俾hk free press<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/support-hkfp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fsupport-hkfp%2F&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=42e77ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/support-hkfp/</a><br />\n<br />\n題外話：rthk都有英文新聞架，都唔錯架！喺民記直播聽到 rthk d 記者姐姐英文勁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75eb8f8b434a7e719f4b8cc83edc195da99493ac","tid":1488320,"uid":220977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"Rthk打手"},{"pid":"6eaa9c8b1294c163a641ef98a9aaace8df0a3d0f","tid":1488320,"uid":220977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"支持立場"},{"pid":"445e52707a5194b14567e4826cb01e2f1114c5ce","tid":1488320,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8459e5cdb8fb60e1d559283240370301dc441f3c","tid":1488320,"uid":220977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"Hong kong free press 都撐"},{"pid":"d239239886370b06bd245644061bd66938e5ffe1","tid":1488320,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64d01ccc9cce4431f35e35ee6def5439c89fcddf","tid":1488320,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"Self push 10 times"},{"pid":"35a60f67d0aba56ff9ab2f7b83ce1c1eab46cab2","tid":1488320,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,